OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few showers around in the
OL,6,Fmorning but still plenty of dry and
OL,7,Fbright spells. Drier in the afternoon
OL,8,Falthough the odd shower still possible
OL,9,Fwith longer sunny spells developing.
OL,10,FMostly light northerly winds but
OL,11,Fbreezy near northern coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be a mostly dry
OL,14,Fevening with some late sunny spells,
OL,15,Fthen largely clear overnight. Cloudier
OL,16,Fwith the odd shower over Caithness and
OL,17,FSutherland. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
