OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FDry start with sunny spells.
OL,6,FTurning cloudy through the morning
OL,7,Fwith rain spreading eastwards. Rain
OL,8,Fheavier in the west with northern and
OL,9,Feastern areas dry for much of the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,13,Fcloudy with heavy showers on Sunday.
OL,14,FDrier on Monday with sunny spells, the
OL,15,Fodd shower possible. Strong winds at
OL,16,Ftimes Tuesday with rain clearing to
OL,17,Fheavy showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
